WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Welcome to reef patterns and mathematics!

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000
The Great Barrier Reef is full of amazing patterns we can explore.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Coral grows in beautiful geometric shapes and sequences.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Let's discover how patterns help us understand marine life.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Count with us as we explore the wonders beneath the waves!